{"tid":1789000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「溫暖一下子傳遞到全身」商台女記者忍唔住笑","createTime":"2019-12-19T06:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:44:44.000Z","uid":265371,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1bdf6e299d97262341ef622d313d448bbe1b59","tid":1789000,"uid":265371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"【澳門中一生形容與習近平握手「溫暖一下子傳遞到全身」】<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平到訪澳門第二日，早上到濠江中學附屬英才學校參觀。<br />\n<br />\n有初中學生説，以為習近平很嚴肅，但發現對方和藹可親，他形容與習近平握手後，溫暖一下子傳遞到全身，對方亦將自己抱入懷中，感到特別幸福，習近平勉勵他好好學習、天天向上，一定要學好中國歷史。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #習近平 #澳門 #濠江中學附屬英才學校<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3069198569854845/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3069198569854845%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=3bd54ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3069198569854845/</a><br />\n<br />\n忍笑忍得好Cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qezHwB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqezHwB2.png&h=cd70f7e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2aaaca438e6891a522e88303c8d7d8a1da88372","tid":1789000,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"肛門感受到習大大熱棒既溫暖"},{"pid":"7be1af3e8f43860096c2a9235ade4d82cb0dfd98","tid":1789000,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"嬌軀一抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8402c73deed31dadef661efa42e5f7fb59ae8bd6","tid":1789000,"uid":12412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-1